trans-unit.source: A Windows Forms control that can be used to host a Windows Presentation Foundation (WPF) element.
trans-unit.target: Control de Windows Forms que se puede usar para hospedar un elemento de Windows Presentation Foundation (WPF).

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> control to place a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> on your [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] control or form.
trans-unit.target: Use la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> control se coloque una [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> en su [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] control o formulario.

trans-unit.source: To host a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] control in a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] element, use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> element.
trans-unit.target: Al host una [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] controlar en un [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] elemento, use la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> elemento.

trans-unit.source: WindowsFormsIntegration.dll is installed with the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] assemblies.
trans-unit.target: WindowsFormsIntegration.dll se instala con el [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] ensamblados.

trans-unit.source: The default location for the assembly is %programfiles%\Reference Assemblies\Microsoft\Framework\v3.0\WindowsFormsIntegration.dll.
trans-unit.target: La ubicación predeterminada para el ensamblado es %programfiles%\Reference Assemblies\Microsoft\Framework\v3.0\WindowsFormsIntegration.dll.

trans-unit.source: To host a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] element in a Windows Form, you must assign the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] element to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Al host una [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] elemento en un formulario Windows Forms, debe asignar el [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] elemento a la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.PropertyMap%2A> property to assign custom mappings between an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> control and its hosted [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] element.
trans-unit.target: Use la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.PropertyMap%2A> propiedad para asignar las asignaciones personalizadas entre un <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> control y sus hospedada [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] elemento.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Windows Forms and WPF Property Mapping](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/windows-forms-and-wpf-property-mapping.md).
trans-unit.target: Para más información, vea [Asignación de propiedades en formularios Windows Forms y WPF](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/windows-forms-and-wpf-property-mapping.md).

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> control to host a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] element.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the control is automatically resized to display its entire contents.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece un valor que indica si el control cambia automáticamente de tamaño para mostrar todo su contenido.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the control adjusts its size to closely fit its contents; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si el control ajusta su tamaño al contenido; en caso contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es <see langword="true" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the hosted element has a transparent background.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece un valor que indica si el elemento hospedado tiene un fondo transparente.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the hosted element has a transparent background; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si el elemento hospedado tiene un fondo transparente; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.BackColorTransparent%2A> property enables bitmap copying, which enables hosted elements to use transparency over the host container.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.BackColorTransparent%2A> propiedad permite copiar el mapa de bits, lo que permite hospeda elementos para utilizar la transparencia en el contenedor del host.

trans-unit.source: This is useful when the element is over an image or gradient background.
trans-unit.target: Esto es útil cuando el elemento está por encima de una imagen o un fondo degradado.

trans-unit.source: For performance reasons, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.BackColorTransparent%2A> property is turned off by default.
trans-unit.target: Por motivos de rendimiento, la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.BackColorTransparent%2A> propiedad está desactivada de forma predeterminada.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <see langword="false" /> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> para liberar tanto recursos administrados como no administrados; es <see langword="false" /> para liberar únicamente recursos no administrados.

trans-unit.source: Immediately frees any system resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Libera inmediatamente todos los recursos del sistema utilizados por el control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost" />.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose` method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Se llama a este método público `Dispose` método y <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: `Dispose` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose` se invoca el protegido `Dispose(Boolean)` método con el `disposing` parámetro establecido en `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invoca `Dispose` con `disposing` establecido en `false`.

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> references.
trans-unit.target: Cuando el parámetro `disposing` es `true`, este método libera todos los recursos retenidos por los objetos administrados a los que el control <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> hace referencia.

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Este método invoca al método `Dispose` de cada uno de los objetos a los que se hace referencia.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="Dispose" /> can be called multiple times by other objects.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Dispose" /> puede recibir varias llamadas de otros objetos.

trans-unit.source: When overriding <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" /> be careful not to reference objects that have been previously disposed of in an earlier call to <see langword="Dispose" />.
trans-unit.target: Al reemplazar <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" /> tenga cuidado de no hacer referencia a objetos que se hayan eliminado en una llamada anterior a <see langword="Dispose" />.

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to implement <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, see [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información sobre cómo implementar <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, consulte [implementa un método Dispose](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).

trans-unit.source: For more information about <see langword="Dispose" /> and <see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) and [Overriding the Finalize Method](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información acerca de <see langword="Dispose" /> y <see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />, consulte [limpiar recursos no administrados](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) y [reemplazar el método Finalize](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/includes/tlasharptla-winclient-md.md)] window to be opened modelessly.
trans-unit.target: Ventana de [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/includes/tlasharptla-winclient-md.md)] que se va a abrir de forma no modal.

trans-unit.source: Enables a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Window" /> to receive keyboard messages correctly when it is opened modelessly from [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Permite al objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Window" /> recibir correctamente los mensajes de teclado cuando se abre de forma no modal en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Call the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.EnableModelessKeyboardInterop%2A> method to forward all keyboard messages when a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] window is opened modelessly.
trans-unit.target: Llame a la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.EnableModelessKeyboardInterop%2A> método para reenviar todos los mensajes de teclado cuando un [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] ventana se abre de forma no modal.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.EnableModelessKeyboardInterop%2A> method installs a message filter in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)]-based application.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.EnableModelessKeyboardInterop%2A> método instala un filtro de mensajes en el [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)]-aplicación basada en.

trans-unit.source: The filter forwards all keyboard messages when the modeless window is active.
trans-unit.target: El filtro reenvía todos los mensajes de teclado cuando la ventana no modal está activa.

trans-unit.source: If a key message is not handled by the hosted [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] element, it is forwarded up the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] class hierarchy for processing.
trans-unit.target: Si no se controla un mensaje de tecla por hospedado [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] elemento, éste se reenvía a la [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] clase jerarquía para su procesamiento.

trans-unit.source: Processes a mnemonic character, ensuring that the hosted element has an opportunity to handle the mnemonic before normal [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] processing.
trans-unit.target: Procesa un carácter de tecla de acceso, asegurando que el elemento hospedado tiene oportunidad de controlar la tecla de acceso antes de que [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] se procese normalmente.

trans-unit.source: Gets the property map, which determines how setting properties on the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost" /> control affects the hosted [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/includes/tlasharptla-winclient-md.md)] element.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el mapa de propiedades, que determina cómo la configuración de las propiedades en el control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost" /> afecta al elemento hospedado de [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/includes/tlasharptla-winclient-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap" /> that maps <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost" /> to properties on the hosted [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] element.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap" /> que asigna <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost" /> a las propiedades del elemento hospedado de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] technologies have two similar but different property models.
trans-unit.target: El [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] y [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] tecnologías tienen dos modelos de propiedades similares pero diferentes.

trans-unit.source: *Property mapping* supports interoperation between the two architectures.
trans-unit.target: *Asignación de propiedad* admite la interoperación entre las dos arquitecturas.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Windows Forms and WPF Property Mapping](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/windows-forms-and-wpf-property-mapping.md).
trans-unit.target: Para más información, vea [Asignación de propiedades en formularios Windows Forms y WPF](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/windows-forms-and-wpf-property-mapping.md).

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.PropertyMap%2A> property to translate the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Margin%2A> property for a hosted [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] element.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo de código siguiente se muestra cómo utilizar el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.PropertyMap%2A> propiedad para traducir el <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Margin%2A> propiedad hospedados [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] elemento.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Walkthrough: Mapping Properties Using the ElementHost Control](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/walkthrough-mapping-properties-using-the-elementhost-control.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información, consulte [Tutorial: propiedades de asignación mediante el ElementHost Control](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/walkthrough-mapping-properties-using-the-elementhost-control.md).

trans-unit.source: Occurs during a drag-and-drop operation and enables the drag source to determine whether the drag-and-drop operation should be canceled.
trans-unit.target: Se produce durante una operación de arrastrar y colocar, y permite al origen de arrastre determinar si la operación de arrastrar y colocar tiene que cancelarse.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.QueryContinueDrag> event, see <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.QueryContinueDrag?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información sobre el evento <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.QueryContinueDrag>, vea <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.QueryContinueDrag?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.target: Factor de escala para el eje X.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to specify the direction of the control to select; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> para especificar la dirección del control que se va a seleccionar; en caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to move forward in the tab order; <see langword="false" /> to move backward in the tab order.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> para moverse hacia delante en el orden de tabulación; es <see langword="false" /> para moverse hacia atrás en el orden de tabulación.

trans-unit.source: Activates the hosted element.
trans-unit.target: Activa el elemento hospedado.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Select%2A> method activates the hosted element.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Select%2A> método activa el elemento hospedado.

trans-unit.source: If more than one hosted element exists, either the first or last element is activated, depending on the `directed` and `forward` parameters.
trans-unit.target: Si existe más de un elemento hospedado, se activa el elemento primero o último, según la `directed` y `forward` parámetros.

trans-unit.source: Repeated calls to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Select%2A> method do not traverse the hosted elements.
trans-unit.target: Las llamadas repetidas a la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Select%2A> método no atraviesan los elementos hospedados.

trans-unit.source: To select subsequent elements, call the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.MoveFocus%2A> method on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.HostContainer%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Para seleccionar los elementos subsiguientes, llame a la <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.MoveFocus%2A> método en el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.HostContainer%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: This implementation forwards tab keys from [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/includes/tlasharptla-winclient-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Esta implementación reenvía las teclas tab de [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/includes/tlasharptla-winforms-md.md)] a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/includes/tlasharptla-winclient-md.md)].
